     C*
     C                     MOVELK@YYYY    W@YYYY
     C                     MOVEL'/'       W@SLSH
     C                     MOVELK@MMMM    W@MMMM
     C                     MOVELW@YYMM    C2YYMM
     C                     Z-ADDW@DAYS    C2DAYS
     C*
     C           *LOVAL    SETLLANYWP11
     C*
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C*
